quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Pali dzuwa ndi kuwala kwake
  91,2,Ndi pali mwezi umene umatuluka dzuwa litalowa
  91,3,Ndi masana pamene kumayera
  91,4,Ndi pali usiku umene umabisa
  91,5,Ndi pali Kumwamba ndi Iye amene adakulenga
  91,6,Ndi pali dziko lapansi ndi Iye amene analitambasula
  91,7,Ndi pali mzimu ndi Iye amene adaulenga
  91,8,Ndi kumupatsa iye nzeru zodziwa choipa ndi chabwino
  91,9,Ndithudi wopambana ndi amene amadziyeretsa
  91,10,Ndipo wolephera ndiye amene wadzidetsa
  91,11,Anthu a Thamoud adakana Mtumwi wawo poukiramoyerekedwa
  91,12,Pamenemunthuolakwakwambiri adayambitsa chipolowe
  91,13,"Ndipo Mthenga wa Mulungu anati kwa iwo: “Samalirani ngamira ya ikazi ya Mulungu ndi tsiku lake lomwa madzi!”"
  91,14,Iwo sadakhulupirire ayi ndipo ngamirayo adaipha. Motero Ambuye wawo adawaononga chifukwa cha machimo awo ndipo adafafaniza onse mosasankha
  91,15,Iye sadaope chotsatira chake